Dear {{agent_name}},

I recently came across your listing for {{property_address}} and I'm very interested in learning more about this property.

Could you please provide additional information about its current condition, including any recent renovations or issues I should be aware of? I noticed that it was previously under contract but has returned to the market, I'm curious about why the previous contract fell through - were there any inspection concerns or other factors?

Also, I would appreciate if you could share more pictures of both the interior and exterior of the home.

Thank you for your assistance. I look forward to your response.

Best regards,
{{your_name}}
{{your_phone}}
{{your_email}}
